Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.82,0:00:10.66,Default,Woman,0,0,0,,Watch your step.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.73,0:00:17.62,Default,Woman,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.62,0:00:19.73,Default,Woman,0,0,0,,Take it slow, take it slow.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.24,0:00:30.71,Bengoshi-Hakamada_Window_Sign,Words,0,0,0,,Hakamada Law Office
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.71,0:00:35.18,Bengoshi-Hakamada_Window_Sign,Words,0,0,0,,{\a6}{\fs20}Hakamada Law Office
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.18,0:00:37.64,Default,Yoshie,0,0,0,,I won chocolate at pachinko. Want some?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.64,0:00:39.37,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.37,0:00:41.18,Default,Rina,0,0,0,,I want some, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.18,0:00:43.52,Default,Yoshie,0,0,0,,Say, Kanae-chan, wanna go \Nget a drink together?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.65,0:00:46.89,Bengoshi-Credits_Left,Caption,0,0,0,,{\fad(380,380)}Assistant of Hakamada\N Nonomura Kanae
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.30,0:00:45.88,Bengoshi-Top,Kanae,0,0,0,,It's only four o'clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.88,0:00:47.09,Bengoshi-Top,Kanae,0,0,0,,I'm still working.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.09,0:00:49.72,Bengoshi-Credits,Caption,0,0,0,,{\fad(380,0)}Temp\N Shinozuka Rina
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.09,0:00:49.73,Bengoshi-Top,Rina,0,0,0,,I don't think anyone \Nwill show up this late.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.34,0:00:53.33,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,Maybe we should invite Sensei, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.86,0:00:56.67,Default,Yoshie,0,0,0,,He doesn't drink, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.67,0:00:59.29,Default,Yoshie,0,0,0,,He'd be no fun at all if he came along.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.56,0:01:04.77,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,I wonder what he does for fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.77,0:01:06.51,Default,Rina,0,0,0,,Making bread, for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.51,0:01:08.24,Bengoshi-Top,Rina,0,0,0,,He once said to me, completely serious,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.64,0:01:10.05,Bengoshi-Credits,Caption,0,0,0,,{\fad(380,380)}Attorney \NHakamada Yukio
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.24,0:01:11.31,Bengoshi-Top,Rina,0,0,0,,"Flour is my lover."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.31,0:01:15.18,Default,Yoshie,0,0,0,,His relationship with his lover \Nisn't making any progress.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.45,0:01:13.98,Bengoshi-Yoshie_Credits,Caption,0,0,0,,{\fad(380,380)}Office landlord \NToyama Yoshie
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.18,0:01:18.39,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,I wonder why Sensei never got married?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.39,0:01:22.53,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,After all, he's a lawyer, \Nhe's tall, and his looks...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.53,0:01:25.02,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,Well, they aren't too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.02,0:01:28.10,Default,Yoshie,0,0,0,,{\i1}You{\i0} should marry him, then, Kanae-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.10,0:01:29.57,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.57,0:01:30.93,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,Impossible, impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.93,0:01:32.27,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,No way, no way!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.27,0:01:33.79,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.79,0:01:35.37,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,What's impossible?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.37,0:01:38.61,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,What? Oh, nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.97,0:01:40.91,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.34,0:01:43.41,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,Are you here for legal counseling?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.41,0:01:46.11,Bengoshi-Credits_Left,Caption,0,0,0,,{\fad(380,0)}This episode's client \NSuwa Natsuki
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.41,0:01:46.11,Bengoshi-Top,Natsuki,0,0,0,,I don't have an appointment. \NIs that okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.11,0:01:46.70,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.70,0:01:48.17,Default,Rina,0,0,0,,No problem at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.17,0:01:50.99,Default,Rina,0,0,0,,Sensei's schedule has been \Nempty for the past three days.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.99,0:01:52.22,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,Too much information.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.22,0:01:53.35,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,Please, this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.35,0:01:54.72,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,Sensei, we have a client.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.72,0:01:55.26,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.93,0:01:56.94,Default,Yoshie,0,0,0,,Sensei, get tea!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.94,0:01:57.99,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.82,0:02:02.85,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.85,0:02:03.70,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.70,0:02:07.24,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Please tell me about \Nwhy you're here today.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.11,0:02:10.69,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,My father...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.55,0:02:14.51,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,is being deceived.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.35,0:02:16.77,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,And how is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.14,0:02:19.71,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,My mother passed away \Nabout three years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.71,0:02:24.67,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,My father remarried a year \Nafter that, to Chika-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.22,0:02:27.72,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,I am financially independent.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.72,0:02:31.01,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Who my father marries doesn't affect me...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.49,0:02:32.88,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.88,0:02:35.73,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Chika-san is younger than me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.15,0:02:38.47,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,What are their ages?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.47,0:02:45.10,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Chika-san is 27, my father is 72.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.10,0:02:48.45,Default,Rina,0,0,0,,So she's 45 years his junior.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.99,0:02:51.34,Default,Yoshie,0,0,0,,I'm jealous.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.34,0:02:55.28,Default,Yoshie,0,0,0,,I want to be with a younger man, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.28,0:02:57.52,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,Don't butt in, you two!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.90,0:03:02.96,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,However, I suspect Chika-san \Nmarried my father for his money.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.96,0:03:04.32,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Why do you suspect that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.32,0:03:07.57,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Chika-san buys brand-name\N goods almost daily.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.57,0:03:10.20,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,She goes on weekend \Ntrips with her friends,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.20,0:03:12.33,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,leaving my father behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.33,0:03:15.28,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Of course my father pays for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.11,0:03:19.02,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,It's been approximately two years \Nsince they were married...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.02,0:03:22.22,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,But I believe he's spent at least \N30 million yen on her in that time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.22,0:03:23.73,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,30 million...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.73,0:03:26.64,Default,Yoshie,0,0,0,,Your father must be rich.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.64,0:03:28.86,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,He's retired now,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.86,0:03:31.72,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,but he ran his own \Ncivil engineering firm.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.72,0:03:33.14,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.14,0:03:34.64,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,So in other words, Natsuki-san,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.64,0:03:36.52,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,you want your father to get a divorce.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.52,0:03:37.43,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.43,0:03:40.86,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,She's already begun\N the divorce process.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.86,0:03:42.76,Default,Yoshie,0,0,0,,The wife?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.76,0:03:46.02,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,She is suing for five million \Nyen in compensation.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.02,0:03:47.23,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Five million?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.77,0:03:48.82,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,On what grounds?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.82,0:03:52.01,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,She insists my father \Nis cheating on her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.01,0:03:53.87,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,She has evidence, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.79,0:04:02.06,Default,Yoshie,0,0,0,,Caught red-handed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.06,0:04:06.30,Default,Rina,0,0,0,,Occasionally, there are old men \Nin their seventies who are still feisty.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.92,0:04:08.58,Default,Yoshie,0,0,0,,But, don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.58,0:04:10.45,Default,Yoshie,0,0,0,,Despite his looks,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.45,0:04:12.98,Default,Yoshie,0,0,0,,Sensei's a specialist when it \Ncomes to compensation lawsuitsー
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.98,0:04:14.91,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,I am sorry to say,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.91,0:04:17.11,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,but I must refuse this case.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.62,0:04:19.76,Default,Rina,0,0,0,,Why is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.76,0:04:25.98,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,That man is the most \Ndisreputable man in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.51,0:04:29.81,Default,Yoshie,0,0,0,,You know him, Sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.81,0:04:30.94,Default,R,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.94,0:04:33.55,Default,R,0,0,0,,My father, Suwa Kozo,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.14,0:04:37.15,Default,R,0,0,0,,is also Hakamada-sensei's father.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.15,0:04:38.31,Default,All,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.73,0:04:58.83,Bengoshi-Title,,0,0,0,,Divorce Chaser\N{\fs25}~Let's Turn Your Tears into Money~
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.17,0:05:03.94,Bengoshi-Ep_Title,Caption left,0,0,0,,Divorce Chaser Episode 6 \NHakamada's Shocking Past Revealed!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.94,0:05:08.90,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,If Natsuki-san's father is \NHakamada-sensei's father...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.90,0:05:13.17,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,I am Sensei's younger half-sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.69,0:05:17.76,Default,Yoshie,0,0,0,,You don't look like him at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.11,0:05:23.61,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,My father divorced his \Nmother thirty years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.79,0:05:27.80,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,I know I shouldn't force \Nhim into a case such as this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.80,0:05:33.13,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,But, I've discussed this \Ncase with other lawyers,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.13,0:05:37.87,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,and they all said it would be difficult \Nto avoid the lawsuit due to the evidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.99,0:05:42.06,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,While I was searching for a lawyer,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.06,0:05:45.88,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,I came across Hakamada-sensei, \Na specialist in divorce issues.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.88,0:05:51.72,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Then, I found out he's is the son \Nof my father and his former wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.55,0:05:58.06,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,So I thought he would be the only \None suitable to take this case.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.36,0:06:01.16,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Please, Sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.67,0:06:04.30,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Please protect our father.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.47,0:06:11.20,Default,Kurumi,0,0,0,,So he turned his sister down?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.20,0:06:14.70,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,Yes, Sensei was quite firm about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.84,0:06:16.24,Bengoshi-Credits_Kurumi,Caption,0,0,0,,{\fad(380,380)}Freelance Investigator \N Umemoto Kurumi
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.70,0:06:17.57,Default,Kurumi,0,0,0,,He must have a grudge \Nagainst his father.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.56,0:06:20.25,Default,Rina,0,0,0,,We've got trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.25,0:06:20.96,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.96,0:06:23.18,Default,Rina,0,0,0,,Sensei's bread is delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.18,0:06:25.65,Default,Kurumi,0,0,0,,That's not possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.80,0:06:34.32,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,You're right. It's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.32,0:06:35.55,Default,Kurumi,0,0,0,,Not good...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.55,0:06:37.01,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.01,0:06:40.29,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,It turned out quite well \Ncompared to his usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.29,0:06:42.14,Default,Kurumi,0,0,0,,That's not what I mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.14,0:06:45.69,Default,Kurumi,0,0,0,,If Sensei's bread is good,\N it means he's very distressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.69,0:06:46.99,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.99,0:06:50.46,Default,Kurumi,0,0,0,,When the water pipes burst \Nand flooded his home,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.46,0:06:51.78,Default,Kurumi,0,0,0,,he got quite distressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.78,0:06:54.95,Default,Kurumi,0,0,0,,The bread he made during that \Ntime was really delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.73,0:06:58.75,Default,Rina,0,0,0,,That must be what it takes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.11,0:07:02.95,Default,Kurumi,0,0,0,,I won't have any work to do if \NSensei stays in this condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.82,0:07:05.62,Default,Kurumi,0,0,0,,I'm going home.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.76,0:07:12.78,Bengoshi-Flashback,Natsuki,0,0,0,,It's too bad you won't accept the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.78,0:07:17.50,Bengoshi-Flashback,Natsuki,0,0,0,,However, Father did want to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.50,0:07:19.66,Bengoshi-Flashback,Hakamada,0,0,0,,I have no intention of seeing him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.06,0:07:22.79,Bengoshi-Flashback,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Please tell him I said that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.79,0:07:24.21,Bengoshi-Flashback,Natsuki,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.21,0:07:28.04,Bengoshi-Flashback,Hakamada,0,0,0,,He left me and my mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.74,0:07:31.18,Bengoshi-Flashback,Natsuki,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.53,0:07:34.24,Bengoshi-Flashback,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.97,0:07:43.99,Default,Kurumi,0,0,0,,Who do you think you're \Nfeeling up, you perv?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.99,0:07:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.42,0:07:48.35,Default,Kurumi,0,0,0,,This geezer tried to cop a feel!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.05,0:07:50.44,Default,Kozo,0,0,0,,You've got it all wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.44,0:07:53.99,Default,Kozo,0,0,0,,I was brushing the dust off your butt.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.99,0:07:55.39,Default,Rina,0,0,0,,The feisty old man...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.39,0:07:57.16,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,Kurumi-san, that's him!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.16,0:07:58.00,Default,Kurumi,0,0,0,,This is who?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.00,0:07:59.58,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,That's Hakamada-sensei's father.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.58,0:08:00.28,Default,Kurumi,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.55,0:08:04.39,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.97,0:08:08.42,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,What are you doing here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.42,0:08:10.89,Default,Kozo,0,0,0,,Hey, Yukio. Long time no see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.89,0:08:13.86,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,I have turned down your daughter's case.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.79,0:08:17.16,Bengoshi-Credits_Left,Caption,0,0,0,,{\fad(380,380)}Hakamada's father\N Suwa Kozo
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.86,0:08:15.65,Bengoshi-Top,Kozo,0,0,0,,Never mind that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.65,0:08:18.46,Bengoshi-Top,Kozo,0,0,0,,I came to see you today.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.46,0:08:21.09,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,I told her I didn't want to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.09,0:08:22.21,Default,Kozo,0,0,0,,Oh, don't say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.21,0:08:25.07,Default,Kozo,0,0,0,,Let's toast to our reunion.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.89,0:08:27.60,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,I don't drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.13,0:08:30.82,Default,Kozo,0,0,0,,You, too, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.82,0:08:32.54,Default,Kozo,0,0,0,,You can make an exception today.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.54,0:08:35.86,Default,Kozo,0,0,0,,Right? Miss, bring \Nus a couple glasses.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.86,0:08:36.86,Default,Rina,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.86,0:08:39.21,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Don't order around my employees!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.21,0:08:44.75,Default,Kozo,0,0,0,,Look at you, running \Nthis outstanding office.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.75,0:08:45.90,Default,Kozo,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.22,0:08:48.86,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,I never offered you a seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.86,0:08:53.07,Default,Kozo,0,0,0,,A man is the master of his \Nown castle, as they say.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.07,0:08:58.16,Default,Kozo,0,0,0,,After I quit being a contractor \Nand started my civil engineering firm,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.16,0:09:00.12,Default,Kozo,0,0,0,,I sure had a lot of hardship.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.12,0:09:02.61,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,I don't care about your war stories.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.66,0:09:07.06,Default,Kozo,0,0,0,,By the way, which one of \Nthese are you diddling?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.06,0:09:07.86,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.86,0:09:09.87,Default,Kozo,0,0,0,,Look at all these young women.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.87,0:09:11.51,Default,Kozo,0,0,0,,You must be diddling \Nat least one of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.00,0:09:13.85,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,I am not like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.85,0:09:15.92,Default,Kozo,0,0,0,,Want me to guess which one?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.92,0:09:18.02,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,This isn't a quiz show!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.02,0:09:21.47,Default,Kozo,0,0,0,,If you're anything like me, \Nyou go for the good looks.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.36,0:09:25.71,Default,Kozo,0,0,0,,You.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.71,0:09:26.76,Default,Kurumi,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.43,0:09:29.73,Default,Kozo,0,0,0,,You're a bit large. \NCan you move out of the way?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.50,0:09:34.50,Default,Kozo,0,0,0,,There. She's the one.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.50,0:09:36.27,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,What? No, I'm not.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.27,0:09:37.73,Default,Kozo,0,0,0,,It's not you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.73,0:09:39.51,Default,Kozo,0,0,0,,Too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.51,0:09:40.64,Default,Kozo,0,0,0,,Are you single?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.64,0:09:42.83,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,Yes, you could say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.83,0:09:44.83,Default,Kozo,0,0,0,,How about we go on a date?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.83,0:09:45.46,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.46,0:09:46.92,Default,Kozo,0,0,0,,I'll be a free man soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.92,0:09:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,No, that's a little...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.12,0:09:49.73,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,That's enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.07,0:09:52.28,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Don't you have more pressing concerns?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.28,0:09:55.00,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,You're being sued for compensation \Nfor adultery, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.00,0:09:57.64,Default,Kozo,0,0,0,,Natuski's the one raising \Nall the fuss, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.64,0:09:59.92,Default,Kozo,0,0,0,,I'm going to give Chika what she wants.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.82,0:10:01.81,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.81,0:10:03.45,Default,Kozo,0,0,0,,I've got no excuses.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.89,0:10:05.09,Default,Kozo,0,0,0,,Besides, I'm a man,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.09,0:10:08.45,Default,Kozo,0,0,0,,I don't go chasing after \Nwomen that run from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.04,0:10:12.55,Default,Kozo,0,0,0,,Instead, I wish her nothing but happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.99,0:10:14.99,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Her happiness?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.41,0:10:17.77,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Where do you get off saying that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.77,0:10:20.63,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Have you forgotten what \Nyou did to my mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.63,0:10:22.75,Default,Kozo,0,0,0,,That was thirty years ago, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.17,0:10:27.06,Default,Rina,0,0,0,,Enjoy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.06,0:10:29.64,Default,Kozo,0,0,0,,Anyway, let's make a toast.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.64,0:10:31.49,Default,Yoshie,0,0,0,,I'll have a drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.49,0:10:33.52,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,Yoshie-san, when did you get there?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.52,0:10:36.23,Default,Yoshie,0,0,0,,I smelled fine wine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.78,0:10:41.28,Default,Yoshie,0,0,0,,By the way, I'm the landlord \Nhere, Toyama Yoshie.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.12,0:10:45.40,Default,Kozo,0,0,0,,You're no ordinary woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.40,0:10:48.89,Default,Kozo,0,0,0,,You're brimming with hidden eroticism.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.89,0:10:51.07,Default,Yoshie,0,0,0,,You know me well, daddy-o.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.07,0:10:52.46,Default,Yoshie,0,0,0,,Care to try me out?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.46,0:10:53.33,Default,Kozo,0,0,0,,Sounds good.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.33,0:10:54.64,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.64,0:10:57.45,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,I have nothing to talk to you about.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.45,0:11:00.22,Default,Kozo,0,0,0,,We haven't seen each other for thirty years.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.22,0:11:01.72,Default,Kozo,0,0,0,,There must be tons of \Nstuff to talk about.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.72,0:11:03.72,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,You neglected us for thirty years.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.72,0:11:06.12,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,It's too late to play the father role.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.12,0:11:10.19,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,You and I are complete strangers.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.22,0:11:13.40,Default,Kozo,0,0,0,,You're making this hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.40,0:11:14.14,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Get out.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.14,0:11:14.82,Default,Kozo,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.82,0:11:15.81,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.81,0:11:19.67,Default,Kozo,0,0,0,,But the wine... I brought wine...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.62,0:11:20.11,Bengoshi-Overlap,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Get out. Get out of here now!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.11,0:11:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Get out, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.52,0:11:23.74,Default,Kozo,0,0,0,,What the hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.50,0:11:30.86,Default,Yoshie,0,0,0,,Hakamada-sensei, can I \Ntake this wine home?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.86,0:11:32.21,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Do as you please.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.15,0:11:41.11,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,Sensei seriously hates his father.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.61,0:11:45.92,Default,Yoshie,0,0,0,,Hakamada-sensei had a rough childhood.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.92,0:11:48.97,Default,Yoshie,0,0,0,,That father of his found \Nanother woman at work,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.97,0:11:50.75,Default,Yoshie,0,0,0,,left home, and never came back.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.75,0:11:54.75,Default,Yoshie,0,0,0,,I heard he never paid for compensation \Nor for child support.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.75,0:11:56.99,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,So that's how it was...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.99,0:12:02.56,Default,Yoshie,0,0,0,,His mother raised him all by herself\Nand saved enough to send him to college.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.56,0:12:06.38,Default,Yoshie,0,0,0,,She passed away soon \Nright after he enrolled.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.13,0:12:11.41,Default,Yoshie,0,0,0,,I don't blame him for holding a grudge.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.45,0:12:14.75,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,Yoshie-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.75,0:12:17.86,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,Could it have been it his parents' \Ndivorce that influenced Sensei
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.86,0:12:21.63,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,to become a divorce lawyer?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.43,0:12:24.97,Default,Yoshie,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.33,0:12:27.04,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.49,0:12:28.06,Bengoshi-Overlap,Kanae,0,0,0,,Oh, Natsuki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.06,0:12:30.52,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Did my father come here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.52,0:12:32.82,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,He was just here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.82,0:12:35.04,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,Sensei kicked him out.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.27,0:12:37.17,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.41,0:12:56.93,Bengoshi-Hakamada_Window_Sign2,Words,0,0,0,,Hakamada Law Office
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.70,0:12:45.50,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,I've never seen Sensei so angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.14,0:12:49.04,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,My father is prideful and awkward.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.46,0:12:51.98,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,He must've said\N inappropriate things, as usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.65,0:12:57.36,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,I think his real intention was\N to apologize to Hakamada-sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.36,0:12:58.72,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,Apologize?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.72,0:13:01.02,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Contrary to how he behaves,\N he's contrite.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.36,0:13:07.44,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,He regrets being a deadbeat \Nfather to Hakamada-sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.66,0:13:13.36,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,I was hoping they could overcome \Nthe bad blood between them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.99,0:13:16.87,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,But, it looks like that's \Nnot going to happen...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.28,0:13:20.61,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.14,0:13:27.44,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,Natsuki-san, please wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.79,0:13:28.92,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.53,0:13:32.31,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,I have an idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.90,0:13:37.60,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.60,0:13:39.47,Default,Kozo,0,0,0,,Hey, Yukio.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.47,0:13:41.18,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,You again?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.18,0:13:43.14,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,I told you I am refusing to take the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.14,0:13:44.66,Default,Kozo,0,0,0,,We're not here to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.66,0:13:46.08,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,I was waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.08,0:13:46.73,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.73,0:13:51.01,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,I invited them to use this room\N for divorce consultation.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.01,0:13:52.75,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Why must they do that here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.75,0:13:55.54,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,They are willing to pay \Nfor their time here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.54,0:13:56.72,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,Please, this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.73,0:14:03.53,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,Please, this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.02,0:14:10.86,Bengoshi-Top,Tsujimura,0,0,0,,I am Suwa Chika-san's legal \Nrepresentative, Tsujimura.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.33,0:14:11.63,Bengoshi-Credits,Caption,0,0,0,,{\fad(380,380)}Attorney \NTsujimura
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.30,0:14:15.07,Bengoshi-Credits,Caption,0,0,0,,{\fad(380,0)}Kozo's wife\N Suwa Chika
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.81,0:14:18.64,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,I am Suwa Kozo's daughter, Natsuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.91,0:14:23.04,Default,Tsujimura,0,0,0,,And who is your legal representative?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.04,0:14:24.22,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,We don't have one.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.14,0:14:28.66,Default,Tsujimura,0,0,0,,I had assumed Hakamada-sensei \Nwould be your legal representative.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.66,0:14:32.01,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,I will sit in on behalf of my \Nfather for today's consultation.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.01,0:14:33.92,Default,Tsujimura,0,0,0,,You'll be saving money,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.92,0:14:35.89,Default,Tsujimura,0,0,0,,because hiring a lawyer for \Nthis case would be futile.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.89,0:14:38.65,Default,Kozo,0,0,0,,Whatever, hurry up and start.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.55,0:14:42.22,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,Your father's consultation has begun.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.42,0:14:45.36,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,I don't have a father.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.36,0:14:46.41,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.41,0:14:48.35,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Was this your idea, Kanae-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.35,0:14:49.34,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.34,0:14:51.28,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,That they hold the \Nconsultation at this office.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.28,0:14:55.85,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,So I would overhear their conversation, \Nand jump in to the rescue?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.25,0:14:57.85,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.54,0:15:02.68,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,I don't fall for cheap tricks.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.23,0:15:07.24,Default,Tsujimura,0,0,0,,As I've already informed Kozo-san,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.24,0:15:11.79,Default,Tsujimura,0,0,0,,five million yen will be billed for compensation, \Nin addition to the property distribution.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.79,0:15:12.56,Default,Kozo,0,0,0,,Sounds fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.56,0:15:14.40,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,We will not consent to those terms.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.40,0:15:15.80,Default,Tsujimura,0,0,0,,How is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.80,0:15:19.95,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Chika-san, you married my father \Nfor his wealth, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.95,0:15:20.68,Default,Chika,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.68,0:15:21.87,Default,Kozo,0,0,0,,What are you saying, Natsuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.87,0:15:26.87,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,We have no money to give someone who \Nhas already squandered his fortune.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.87,0:15:29.18,Default,Chika,0,0,0,,You have no right to say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.18,0:15:31.68,Default,Chika,0,0,0,,I have been a devoted wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.68,0:15:33.48,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,What is so devoted about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.48,0:15:37.74,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,I was told you constantly asked \Nfor gifts, without occasion.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.74,0:15:40.21,Default,Kozo,0,0,0,,That's all right. I wanted \Nto give her those gifts.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.21,0:15:41.95,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,They're beyond just gifts!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.95,0:15:43.54,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Two foreign cars,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.54,0:15:46.48,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,co-ownership of a resort mansion,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.48,0:15:50.80,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,and you took him to \Nthat resort only once.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.80,0:15:53.03,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Who were you going there with, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.03,0:15:55.17,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Maybe {\i1}you{\i0} were the one \Nwho was cheating?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.17,0:15:56.77,Default,Chika,0,0,0,,You're just making that up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.77,0:15:58.28,Default,Tsujimura,0,0,0,,Please don't bring up baseless claims.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.28,0:16:03.15,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,And after he married you, \Nmy father's health waned.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.15,0:16:05.71,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Were you taking good care of him?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.71,0:16:06.90,Default,Chika,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.90,0:16:09.52,Default,Tsujimura,0,0,0,,This is Chika-san's blog.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.25,0:16:11.55,Bengoshi-Chika_Blog,Blog title,0,0,0,,Chika's Blog: \NTonight's Loving Wife Dinner
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.52,0:16:13.52,Default,Tsujimura,0,0,0,,You will see here a testament \Nto Chika-san's love of Kozo-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.52,0:16:16.96,Default,Tsujimura,0,0,0,,These are dishes, handmade by\N her for him, every night.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.96,0:16:19.52,Default,Tsujimura,0,0,0,,You're a woman, you should \Nknow how much work that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.52,0:16:24.03,Default,Chika,0,0,0,,Say what you will.\N I loved Kozo-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.97,0:16:27.27,Default,Chika,0,0,0,,But Kozo-san betrayed me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.14,0:16:39.33,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,You're concerned, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.33,0:16:40.79,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.79,0:16:42.98,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,I dropped my ballpoint pen.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.35,0:16:46.47,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,It's in your front pocket.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.42,0:16:52.61,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,There it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.15,0:16:59.46,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Be that as it may, we will not concede.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.46,0:17:01.50,Default,Tsujimura,0,0,0,,You want to battle it \Nout in court, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.50,0:17:02.96,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,In court?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.82,0:17:06.46,Default,Tsujimura,0,0,0,,You can go to trial, but the \Nresults will be the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.46,0:17:09.44,Default,Tsujimura,0,0,0,,We have solid evidence of \Nhis illicit activities.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.44,0:17:11.23,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Those are...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.23,0:17:13.06,Default,Kozo,0,0,0,,I admit, I went to a hotel with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.06,0:17:14.88,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Father, stay out of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.88,0:17:16.75,Default,Kozo,0,0,0,,But, Chika, I'm telling you the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.75,0:17:19.55,Default,Kozo,0,0,0,,I only did her once.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.55,0:17:21.60,Default,Chika,0,0,0,,It's not a matter of \Nhow many times, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.60,0:17:23.71,Default,Tsujimura,0,0,0,,He's making a plain admission of guilt.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.71,0:17:25.84,Default,Tsujimura,0,0,0,,Please stamp and sign this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.49,0:17:26.36,Bengoshi-Divorce_Consulation,Letter,0,0,0,,Divorce Consultation Form
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.84,0:17:27.07,Default,Kozo,0,0,0,,All right—
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.07,0:17:28.07,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.68,0:17:32.56,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Give us some time to think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.91,0:17:37.40,Default,Tsujimura,0,0,0,,We'll give you one week, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.40,0:17:39.84,Default,Tsujimura,0,0,0,,The next time will be \Nour final consultation.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.55,0:17:42.06,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.94,0:17:48.58,Bengoshi-Hakamada_Wood_Plaque,Plaque,0,0,0,,Hakamada \NLaw Office
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.01,0:17:52.29,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Was Hakamada-sensei listening?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.29,0:17:54.76,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,He seemed quite concerned.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.76,0:17:57.94,Default,Kozo,0,0,0,,Forget about it. I don't \Nneed that stubborn fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.94,0:17:59.45,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.45,0:18:00.86,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Bye, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.29,0:18:08.16,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.65,0:18:22.88,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,They're gone now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.88,0:18:24.89,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,You could've at least seen them out.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.89,0:18:28.15,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,I have no relationship with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.15,0:18:31.45,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,And please, don't rent our office space
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.45,0:18:32.74,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,without asking me first.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.74,0:18:35.07,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,What does it matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.07,0:18:37.32,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,You don't have to take \Nthem on as a client...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.32,0:18:40.36,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,But you could've at least listened,\N and given them advice.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.36,0:18:41.81,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Advice?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.62,0:18:44.98,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Then, there's one\N thing I've learned.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.98,0:18:46.07,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.15,0:18:49.68,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,He{\i1} is{\i0} being deceived.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.68,0:18:50.64,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.64,0:18:53.10,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Assuming he was telling the truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.10,0:18:57.23,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,he said he was with his illicit \Npartner for one time only.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.23,0:18:58.64,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.64,0:19:02.94,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Don't you think it's strange\N that she could capture
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.94,0:19:05.34,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,an unexpected one-time \Nevent like that on film?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.34,0:19:06.69,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,That's true...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.69,0:19:09.82,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,Do you think Chika-san and \Nher lawyer are scheming?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.66,0:19:12.19,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,That is possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.19,0:19:16.92,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,If you know that, \Nyou could help your father!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.58,0:19:20.65,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,It is difficult to prove \Nthere was no illicit affair,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.65,0:19:24.56,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,especially since he was photographed\N coming out of the hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.56,0:19:26.14,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,I know you can do it, Sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.14,0:19:27.94,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,Please protect your father.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.94,0:19:30.28,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,I have no reason to protect him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.14,0:19:36.65,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,He has been womanizing all his life.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.49,0:19:41.91,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,My mother and I fell victim to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.83,0:19:45.35,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,He should get what's coming to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.35,0:19:47.08,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.16,0:19:52.76,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Also, he's willing to pay compensation.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.61,0:19:55.42,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,The matter is out of my hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.95,0:20:00.20,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.20,0:20:02.14,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,I'll do it, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.70,0:20:03.97,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Do what?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.97,0:20:07.85,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,I'm going to find proof that \NChika-san's story is a fabrication.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.85,0:20:10.65,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,I'm going to ask Kurumi-san \Nto help me. Is that okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.32,0:20:13.28,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,I don't mind, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.63,0:20:17.35,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,I cannot have you neglect office duties.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.35,0:20:19.80,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,There's nothing to do \Nat this office, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.26,0:20:33.72,Default,Rina,0,0,0,,Um, Sensei...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.72,0:20:34.95,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.95,0:20:37.07,Default,Rina,0,0,0,,Your father forgot something.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.13,0:20:40.88,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,He is not my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.88,0:20:43.30,Default,Rina,0,0,0,,What should I do with it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.58,0:20:45.95,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Shinozuka-san,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.95,0:20:48.31,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,I'm sorry to trouble you,\N but could you deliver it to him?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.31,0:20:50.12,Default,Rina,0,0,0,,No, I won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.74,0:20:52.74,Default,Rina,0,0,0,,He's your father, Sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.74,0:20:54.96,Default,Rina,0,0,0,,You should deliver it to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.72,0:20:58.29,Default,Rina,0,0,0,,There's prescription \Nmedicine in this, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.67,0:21:01.41,Default,Rina,0,0,0,,You should hurry. He might need it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.64,0:21:13.04,Bengoshi-Prescription_Medicine,Medicine bag,0,0,0,,Prescription Medicine\N Mr. Suwa Kozo
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.93,0:21:38.48,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Are you all right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.73,0:21:41.23,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.23,0:21:43.64,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Ambulance.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.64,0:21:45.72,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Someone call an ambulance!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.34,0:21:47.51,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,I am sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.51,0:21:51.61,Default,Misato,0,0,0,,That's unusual. You've never \Nrequested a deadline extension before.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.61,0:21:52.95,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,I'm very sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.95,0:21:55.37,Bengoshi-Top,Kanae,0,0,0,,I'm having writer's block.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.65,0:21:58.19,Bengoshi-Credits_Left,Caption,0,0,0,,{\fad(380,380)}Editor at Tokiwa Publishing\N Tabata Misato
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.37,0:21:58.52,Bengoshi-Top,Misato,0,0,0,,You can't get material \Nfrom the law office?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.52,0:22:00.79,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,There's definitely material,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.79,0:22:04.04,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,but the problem is that \NSensei is refusing to take on a client.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.04,0:22:05.52,Default,Sara,0,0,0,,In that case, there is no problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.52,0:22:06.53,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.16,0:22:09.94,Default,Sara,0,0,0,,I can feel it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.16,0:22:11.20,Bengoshi-Credits,Caption,0,0,0,,{\fad(380,380)}Cafe waitress: \NMizutani Sara
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.09,0:22:13.14,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.14,0:22:15.00,Default,Kurumi,0,0,0,,I found the woman in the photo.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.00,0:22:16.10,Default,Kurumi,0,0,0,,Can you come right away?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.10,0:22:17.25,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.25,0:22:18.80,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. I have to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.80,0:22:19.60,Default,Misato,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.49,0:22:23.78,Default,Sara,0,0,0,,Amazing! I feel it so strongly!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.78,0:22:26.65,Default,Misato,0,0,0,,Um... she left already.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.65,0:22:27.60,Default,Sara,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.29,0:22:40.85,Default,Kozo,0,0,0,,Yukio.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.99,0:22:44.60,Default,Kozo,0,0,0,,Was it you that rescued me?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.37,0:22:49.67,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,I didn't do it for you, particularly.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.86,0:22:55.93,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,I would help anyone who \Nhad collapsed on the street.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.68,0:22:59.94,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,How bothersome.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.94,0:23:04.55,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,I even had to hear what \Nthe doctor had to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.24,0:23:09.89,Default,Kozo,0,0,0,,Don't tell Chika and Natsuki that I'm sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.89,0:23:13.92,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,What's the point of being \Nprideful at a time like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.92,0:23:16.37,Default,Kozo,0,0,0,,You're a complete stranger, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.13,0:23:20.16,Default,Kozo,0,0,0,,What do you care?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.67,0:23:32.91,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,How is our father?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.74,0:23:35.76,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,He had a minor seizure.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.76,0:23:40.17,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,The doctor said he can be \Ndischarged quickly, after he rests.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.17,0:23:41.84,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.74,0:23:46.88,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Regardless, he should stop drinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.88,0:23:47.99,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.99,0:23:50.69,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Father doesn't drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.69,0:23:52.79,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,He's never been able to drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.79,0:23:53.93,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.93,0:23:56.48,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,If he drinks, he falls \Nasleep right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.48,0:24:00.44,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,He only drinks when he's really happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.03,0:24:05.22,Bengoshi-Flashback,Kozo,0,0,0,,Let's make a toast to our reunion.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.99,0:24:07.82,Bengoshi-Flashback,Hakamada,0,0,0,,I don't drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.82,0:24:09.45,Bengoshi-Flashback,Kozo,0,0,0,,You, too, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.47,0:24:13.62,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,I have seen him drunk only three times.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.62,0:24:17.82,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,The first time was when I got \Nfirst place in a piano competition.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.82,0:24:21.82,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,The second time was when his \Nfirm landed a huge contract
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.82,0:24:23.85,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,for building a train station.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.85,0:24:28.70,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,The third time was when \Nyou passed your bar exam.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.55,0:24:30.60,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.20,0:24:33.90,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Though he doesn't show it,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.90,0:24:37.59,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,he's always thinks about you,\N Hakamada-sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.63,0:24:41.34,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,After he found out your \Nwere becoming a lawyer,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.34,0:24:44.49,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,he would check the roster of \Nsuccessful bar examinees, every year.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.05,0:24:49.92,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,I once heard him quarreling with \Nmy mother about you, Sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.66,0:24:53.87,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Because he had spent their \Nmoney without telling her...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.78,0:25:00.82,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,I think he anonymously paid \Nyour college entrance fee.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.70,0:25:04.14,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,That man wouldn't do a thing like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.14,0:25:05.93,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,It's a fact.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.24,0:25:09.24,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,I was at that acutely sensitive age...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.87,0:25:13.27,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,My father would be concerned \Nabout a child other than me...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.27,0:25:15.30,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Though I had never met that child,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.30,0:25:17.88,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,there was a time I was jealous of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.94,0:25:26.15,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Oh, and Sensei. I know you believe \Nmy father is a womanizer...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.15,0:25:31.82,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,But, I don't think he's ever \Ncheated on my mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.62,0:25:35.05,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Now that, I can't believe.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.43,0:25:38.43,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,He was probably just hiding it from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.43,0:25:41.44,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Do you think my father \Nis capable of hiding anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.74,0:25:48.81,Bengoshi-Hakamada_Window_Lrg,Words,0,0,0,,Hakamada
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.17,0:26:04.69,Bengoshi-Flashback,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Though he doesn't show it,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.69,0:26:07.96,Bengoshi-Flashback,Natsuki,0,0,0,,he's always thinks about you,\N Hakamada-sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.39,0:26:11.20,Bengoshi-Flashback,Kanae,0,0,0,,But, I know you can do it, Sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.20,0:26:12.83,Bengoshi-Flashback,Kanae,0,0,0,,Please protect your father.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.81,0:26:21.94,Default,Yoshie,0,0,0,,I see you're immersed in your thoughts.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.94,0:26:23.17,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Yoshie-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.17,0:26:24.41,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,When did you come in?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.41,0:26:26.09,Default,Yoshie,0,0,0,,I've been here the whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.47,0:26:28.88,Default,Yoshie,0,0,0,,You've finally decided to help your father.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.88,0:26:29.88,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.88,0:26:32.52,Default,Yoshie,0,0,0,,Because the only time you listen \Nto music and knead dough
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.52,0:26:35.85,Default,Yoshie,0,0,0,,is when you're thinking \Nabout your client.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.37,0:26:39.53,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,I was thinking of a different client.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.95,0:26:43.30,Default,Yoshie,0,0,0,,Oh? Was there another client in here?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.76,0:26:47.52,Default,Yoshie,0,0,0,,Kanae-chan has been wondering...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.13,0:26:54.57,Default,Yoshie,0,0,0,,if you became a divorce lawyer \N because of your father.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.40,0:26:57.68,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,I wouldn't dismiss that as incorrect.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.50,0:27:00.86,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,If only I had knowledge of the law,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.86,0:27:03.47,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,I could've sued my father
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.47,0:27:09.13,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,for compensation and child support \Nafter he divorced my mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.62,0:27:15.80,Default,Yoshie,0,0,0,,But, you initially went into \Ncorporate law, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.23,0:27:18.18,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,How did you know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.59,0:27:21.68,Default,Yoshie,0,0,0,,I love gossip, that's how.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.70,0:27:30.60,Default,Yoshie,0,0,0,,You've forgiven your father, haven't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.61,0:27:40.07,Default,Kanna,0,0,0,,Oh, please. You're so lecherous.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.07,0:27:42.05,Default,Kanna,0,0,0,,I'll have to punish you next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.87,0:27:48.07,Default,Kurumi,0,0,0,,Are you Murakami Kanna-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.07,0:27:48.97,Default,Kanna,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.97,0:27:50.06,Default,Kanna,0,0,0,,Who are you people?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.06,0:27:52.78,Default,Kurumi,0,0,0,,I'm a freelance investigator, \NUmemoto Kurumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.78,0:27:55.73,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,I'm her assistant, Nonomura Kanae.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.63,0:28:00.50,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,Is that you in this photograph?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.30,0:28:04.71,Bengoshi-Credits_Left,Caption,0,0,0,,{\fad(380,380)}Kozo's illicit partner\N Murakami Kanna
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.55,0:28:05.81,Bengoshi-Top,Kanae,0,0,0,,Can you explain to us why you went \Nto this hotel with Suwa Kozo-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.55,0:28:09.24,Default,Kanna,0,0,0,,I've already explained that to an attorney.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.24,0:28:11.71,Default,Kanna,0,0,0,,His name is Tsujimura-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.71,0:28:14.62,Default,Kurumi,0,0,0,,We need to confirm \Nsome facts on our end.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.62,0:28:16.34,Default,Kurumi,0,0,0,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.63,0:28:23.94,Default,Kanna,0,0,0,,I was at a restaurant, and \NKozo-san started talking to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.73,0:28:27.32,Default,Kanna,0,0,0,,He bought me drinks,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.32,0:28:31.15,Default,Kanna,0,0,0,,then lured me to a hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.15,0:28:35.87,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,Are you sure it was Kozo-san \Nwho started talking to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.87,0:28:36.82,Default,Kanna,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.82,0:28:38.50,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,And was he the one who \Nlured you to the hotel?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.50,0:28:40.08,Default,Kanna,0,0,0,,It was Kozo-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.70,0:28:42.41,Default,Kanna,0,0,0,,Why are you asking?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.41,0:28:47.57,Default,Kurumi,0,0,0,,You're personal acquaintances \Nwith Suwa Chika-san, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.57,0:28:48.57,Default,Kanna,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.92,0:28:50.97,Default,Kanna,0,0,0,,No. I don't know her.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.97,0:28:54.17,Default,Kurumi,0,0,0,,Well, that's strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.17,0:28:59.07,Default,Kurumi,0,0,0,,Weren't the two of you in the same \Nescort service until two years ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.07,0:29:00.25,Default,Kanna,0,0,0,,I don't know her.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.25,0:29:01.67,Default,Kurumi,0,0,0,,Hm...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.67,0:29:04.24,Default,Kurumi,0,0,0,,Maybe she asked you...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.24,0:29:07.15,Default,Kurumi,0,0,0,,...to lure Kozo-san to the hotel?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.15,0:29:09.70,Default,Kanna,0,0,0,,What are you people after?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.70,0:29:12.66,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,We just want to know the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.66,0:29:15.71,Default,Kanna,0,0,0,,Everything I said is true.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.71,0:29:17.08,Default,Kanna,0,0,0,,Now, excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.91,0:29:21.54,Default,Kurumi,0,0,0,,You're not unfamiliar with \Ncases like this, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.07,0:29:25.86,Default,Kurumi,0,0,0,,You have a history of going \Nto hotels with married men.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.86,0:29:28.82,Default,Kurumi,0,0,0,,Every time, they are photographed,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.82,0:29:32.44,Default,Kurumi,0,0,0,,and get sued for compensation\N within a few months.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.44,0:29:34.93,Default,Kurumi,0,0,0,,That's more than just coincidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.93,0:29:39.53,Default,Kurumi,0,0,0,,If you get me started,\N I'll investigate all of your past deeds.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.53,0:29:42.31,Default,Marilyn,0,0,0,,Once I've latched onto my target,\N I never let go.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.31,0:29:43.69,Default,Marilyn,0,0,0,,Because I am...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.69,0:29:46.60,Default,Kurumi,0,0,0,,Freelance Investigator Umemoto Kurumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.11,0:29:52.38,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,Will you speak the truth \Nat the divorce consultation?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.30,0:29:57.81,Default,Kanna,0,0,0,,I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.22,0:30:00.65,Bengoshi-Hakamada_Window_Sign3,Sign,0,0,0,,Hakamada Law Office
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.82,0:30:03.79,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,I am attending Kozo-san's \Nfinal divorce consultation.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.79,0:30:08.13,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,It starts at 2:00, at their lawyer's office.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.13,0:30:10.01,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,Won't you come with me, Sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.01,0:30:13.43,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,No, I have to go somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.43,0:30:14.93,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,And where would that be?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.49,0:30:18.77,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,There's a kind of bread I'm interested in.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.44,0:30:24.89,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,Why must you be so obstinate?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.13,0:30:38.65,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,Thank you for waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.20,0:30:42.63,Default,Kurumi,0,0,0,,Today's consultation will \Ngo well, I assure you.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.63,0:30:44.94,Default,Kurumi,0,0,0,,We've gathered powerful evidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.94,0:30:48.56,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Thank you for all of your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.66,0:30:52.42,Default,Kozo,0,0,0,,Isn't Yukio coming?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.42,0:30:54.97,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,He has other business to attend.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.97,0:30:56.34,Default,Kozo,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.01,0:31:03.11,Default,Waiter,0,0,0,,Would you care for more bread?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.05,0:31:07.98,Default,Waiter,0,0,0,,Would you care for more bread?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.98,0:31:09.79,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,This is good bread.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.79,0:31:11.86,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,It's made with domestic wheat flour.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.86,0:31:13.85,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Probably from Hokkaido.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.85,0:31:14.95,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Am I right?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.95,0:31:17.12,Default,Waiter,0,0,0,,No. It's from Canada.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.33,0:31:19.87,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.70,0:31:22.33,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Oh, one more thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.33,0:31:24.10,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,I have a question.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.57,0:31:27.53,Bengoshi-First_Conference,Plaque,0,0,0,,First Conference Room
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.02,0:31:27.53,Default,Tsujimura,0,0,0,,Have you reached a decision?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.53,0:31:28.20,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.20,0:31:32.16,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,We cannot consent to \Nthis divorce agreement.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.54,0:31:34.18,Default,Tsujimura,0,0,0,,Don't be ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.18,0:31:36.56,Default,Tsujimura,0,0,0,,Kozo-san is clearly guilty \Nof illicit activity.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.56,0:31:38.45,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Concerning that issue...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.27,0:31:40.63,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Chika-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.63,0:31:43.52,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,You know Murakami \NKanna-san here, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.52,0:31:44.42,Default,Chika,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.42,0:31:48.43,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,You were both in the same \Nescort service, weren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.43,0:31:51.48,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Did you ask your friend Kanna-san
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.48,0:31:54.45,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,lure my father to the hotel?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.45,0:31:56.53,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,To have the upper hand in \Nthe divorce consultation?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.53,0:31:58.47,Default,Chika,0,0,0,,I've done no such thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.47,0:31:59.50,Default,Tsujimura,0,0,0,,Can you prove it?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.50,0:32:02.30,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,We have proof.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.30,0:32:05.04,Default,Tsujimura,0,0,0,,Then, show us.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.04,0:32:06.83,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,For that...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.48,0:32:09.37,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,please wait a little while.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.05,0:32:13.47,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,Kanna-san is late.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.34,0:32:17.38,Default,Kurumi,0,0,0,,This is bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.38,0:32:19.91,Default,Kurumi,0,0,0,,She's not picking up.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.91,0:32:23.39,Default,Tsujimura,0,0,0,,When are you producing \Nthis so-called proof?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.59,0:32:23.39,Bengoshi-First_Conference2,Plaque,0,0,0,,First Conference Room
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.39,0:32:25.40,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Please wait just a little longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.42,0:32:33.24,Default,Tsujimura,0,0,0,,Perhaps you are waiting \Nfor Murakami Kanna-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.24,0:32:34.23,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.66,0:32:37.15,Default,Tsujimura,0,0,0,,If it's her you're waiting for, \Nshe won't be coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.15,0:32:38.53,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,How did you...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.53,0:32:41.64,Default,Tsujimura,0,0,0,,Kanna-san contacted me the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.64,0:32:43.63,Default,Tsujimura,0,0,0,,She was very distressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.63,0:32:47.38,Default,Tsujimura,0,0,0,,She said an investigator \Nyou hired blackmailed her,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.38,0:32:48.66,Default,Tsujimura,0,0,0,,and was forcing her\N to fabricate evidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.66,0:32:49.98,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,That's ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.98,0:32:52.68,Default,Tsujimura,0,0,0,,I understand not wanting \Nto pay compensation.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.68,0:32:56.32,Default,Tsujimura,0,0,0,,But your actions are tantamount \Nto the crime of blackmail.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.48,0:33:00.76,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,She's not answering.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.10,0:33:05.02,Default,Kurumi,0,0,0,,Let's forget about Kanna-sa. \NWe need another course of action.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.02,0:33:07.75,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,It's too late for another \Ncourse of action.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.75,0:33:11.31,Default,Tsujimura,0,0,0,,Chika-san is completely innocent \Nwith respect to this divorce.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.31,0:33:13.24,Default,Tsujimura,0,0,0,,Based on various information sources,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.24,0:33:17.20,Default,Tsujimura,0,0,0,,it is clear that Chika-san has \Nbeen a devoted wife to Kozo-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.28,0:33:23.11,Default,Tsujimura,0,0,0,,Please seal and sign \Nthe consultation form.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.73,0:33:27.45,Default,Kozo,0,0,0,,You did what you could, Natsuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.29,0:33:29.92,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.29,0:33:37.15,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,I'm going to go apologize \Nto Natsuki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.13,0:33:45.33,Default,Kurumi,0,0,0,,Kanae-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.10,0:33:56.21,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Please, don't do that just yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.21,0:33:57.69,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Hakamada-sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.69,0:34:00.12,Default,Kozo,0,0,0,,Yukio, what are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.73,0:34:01.65,Default,Tsujimura,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.65,0:34:03.47,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Sorry for not introducing \Nmyself the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.43,0:34:06.62,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,I'm Hakamada, attorney at law.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.62,0:34:09.66,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,I am his assistant, Nonomura Kanae.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.66,0:34:12.85,Default,Tsujimura,0,0,0,,You are Suwa Kozo-san's \Nlegal representative?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.85,0:34:14.20,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.20,0:34:16.35,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,I'm just passing through.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.92,0:34:18.45,Default,Tsujimura,0,0,0,,This is a consultation.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.45,0:34:20.20,Default,Tsujimura,0,0,0,,Please leave if you \Nhave no business here.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.20,0:34:22.56,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,No, he does have business here.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.56,0:34:26.38,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,He's the witness who I invited here.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.38,0:34:27.55,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.55,0:34:31.08,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,He has important information \Npertaining to this consultation.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.24,0:34:35.96,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,I have a question for Chika-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.96,0:34:37.43,Default,Chika,0,0,0,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.77,0:34:43.30,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Did you really love this man?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.30,0:34:44.98,Default,Chika,0,0,0,,Of course I loved him.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.98,0:34:46.66,Default,Chika,0,0,0,,That's why I married him.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.24,0:34:51.65,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,What's so good about this tired,\N lecherous geezer?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.65,0:34:52.60,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.60,0:34:53.64,Default,Kozo,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.64,0:34:56.58,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,He's prideful, he's selfish,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.58,0:35:00.09,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,and, oh yes, his feet \Nsmell utterly horrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.09,0:35:02.28,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Why would you want to \Nmarry a man like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.28,0:35:03.61,Default,Kozo,0,0,0,,What's that supposed to mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:03.61,0:35:08.14,Default,Chika,0,0,0,,When we first met, Kozo-san \Nwas very kind to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.14,0:35:09.69,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,"Kind"?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.69,0:35:12.85,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,You mean he bought you a lot of gifts.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.85,0:35:14.11,Default,Kozo,0,0,0,,What's wrong with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.11,0:35:18.41,Default,Chika,0,0,0,,He's vastly knowledgable, \Nand told me lots of interesting things.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.41,0:35:20.42,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Vastly knowledgable?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.42,0:35:23.89,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,His brain is stuck at \Nmiddle-school level.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.89,0:35:25.80,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,Sensei, what are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.80,0:35:27.73,Default,Kozo,0,0,0,,Did you come here to \Ntalk trash about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.73,0:35:31.57,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Yes. Because you have\N been nothing but trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.57,0:35:33.37,Default,Kozo,0,0,0,,How long must you bear a grudge?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.37,0:35:36.48,Default,Kozo,0,0,0,,You've been a wuss ever \Nsince your were a kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.48,0:35:38.34,Default,Tsujimura,0,0,0,,Take your quarrel somewhere else.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.34,0:35:40.13,Default,Tsujimura,0,0,0,,This is a consultation.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.16,0:35:42.98,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Pardon me.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:42.98,0:35:46.08,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,In that case, one last thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.08,0:35:49.66,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Since you love him so much,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.66,0:35:51.82,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,you know about his sickness, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.82,0:35:52.64,Default,Chika,0,0,0,,Sickness?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.64,0:35:54.69,Default,Kozo,0,0,0,,I told you not to tell her.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.69,0:35:57.66,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Since you seem to not know, \Nlet me explain it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.97,0:36:03.89,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,He has had diabetes for two years.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.67,0:36:08.11,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,But, you cared nothing about that,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.11,0:36:10.88,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,and supposedly made him \Nplenty of rich meals.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.88,0:36:14.73,Default,Chika,0,0,0,,I-It's because I didn't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.73,0:36:16.95,Default,Kozo,0,0,0,,Of course she didn't. I didn't tell her.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.95,0:36:18.58,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.58,0:36:22.85,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Let's say you didn't \Nknow he was diabetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.85,0:36:26.40,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,But, despite being a couple,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.40,0:36:29.59,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,you took no notice of \Nan obvious symptom.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.59,0:36:31.29,Default,Kozo,0,0,0,,Hey, don't you dare.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.29,0:36:38.77,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Suwa Kozo-san has erectile \Ndysfunction from his diabetes.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.77,0:36:40.07,Default,All,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.24,0:36:45.58,Default,Kozo,0,0,0,,Well, not really, you see...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.58,0:36:47.64,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,While I was talking to his doctor,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.64,0:36:49.73,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,I glanced at his medical records.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.60,0:36:53.65,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,He hasn't gotten hard \Nfor two years.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.65,0:36:54.76,Default,Kozo,0,0,0,,Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.76,0:36:55.89,Default,Kozo,0,0,0,,Don't be so explicit!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.89,0:37:00.17,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Maybe that's divine punishment for all \Nthe womanizing in your younger days.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:00.17,0:37:02.88,Default,Kozo,0,0,0,,Shut up, Yukio, or I'll kick your ass right here!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.70,0:37:03.49,Bengoshi-Overlap,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Father! Please be quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.03,0:37:09.19,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Now, would a man like that \Nlure a woman to a hotel?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.33,0:37:11.90,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,He's a prideful man.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.90,0:37:14.49,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,He doesn't want others\N to learn of his weaknesses.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.10,0:37:18.56,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Do you think a man like that \Nwould take a woman to a hotel,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.56,0:37:20.87,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,and make himself \Nvulnerable to ridicule?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.46,0:37:24.03,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,And by the way,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.03,0:37:29.12,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,I spoke to the waiter at the \Nrestaurant where he met Kanna-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.12,0:37:36.57,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,He said he saw Kanna-san put \Nalcohol in his soft drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.57,0:37:38.10,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,As you might know,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.10,0:37:40.52,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,this man does not drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.13,0:37:44.11,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,He immediately became inebriated,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.11,0:37:47.81,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,which made it easier \Nto lure him to the hotel,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.81,0:37:49.62,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,for the purpose of taking evidence photos.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.55,0:37:56.51,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Gold digging and lovelessness aside,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.51,0:38:00.86,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,consider the action of framing \Nyour innocent husband,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.30,0:38:05.64,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,of scheming to steal \Nhis fund for old age.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.47,0:38:11.04,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,I know I'm overstepping my \Nbounds, but let me ask you...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.70,0:38:15.56,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,What is it about you that \Nis a "loving wife"?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.76,0:38:35.78,Default,Rina,0,0,0,,So, Hakamada-sensei came \Nto the rescue after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.78,0:38:39.23,Default,Yoshie,0,0,0,,In spite of being such a sourpuss.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.23,0:38:43.15,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,Thankfully, Chika-san has retracted \Nthe compensation lawsuit,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:43.15,0:38:45.24,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,and there will be no property \Ndistribution, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.24,0:38:47.06,Default,Yoshie,0,0,0,,I see. I'm glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.51,0:38:50.33,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.20,0:38:52.10,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.10,0:38:55.30,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Thank you for everything \Nyou've done for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.30,0:38:56.28,Default,Kozo,0,0,0,,Is Yukio here?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.28,0:38:57.81,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,Sensei is baking bread in the back.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:57.81,0:38:58.84,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Wait, Father...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.84,0:39:01.23,Default,Kozo,0,0,0,,What you did was uncalled for.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.66,0:39:02.79,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,What might that be?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.79,0:39:05.04,Default,Kozo,0,0,0,,I told you not to tell \Nanyone about "that."
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.04,0:39:09.38,Default,Kozo,0,0,0,,I'd rather pay five million yen \Nthan have it revealed.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.38,0:39:10.64,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.64,0:39:12.98,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Stop being so prideful.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.49,0:39:15.91,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Where would you get that kind of money?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.50,0:39:19.86,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,I hear you're scraping the \Nbottom of your savings.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.99,0:39:23.46,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,How do you plan to support \Nyourself in your old age?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.30,0:39:26.03,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,And also...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.03,0:39:30.50,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,it was what you did \Nthat was uncalled for.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.24,0:39:35.79,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,I was going to pay for my \Nown college entrance fee.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.68,0:39:39.20,Default,Kozo,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.71,0:39:43.80,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,You spend money out of pride,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.49,0:39:46.89,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,so now you're broke. Isn't that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.89,0:39:52.60,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Let me just say this...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.85,0:39:59.67,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Thank you for having done that for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.51,0:40:03.27,Default,Kozo,0,0,0,,I don't know what you're talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.27,0:40:05.80,Default,Kozo,0,0,0,,But, hey, how about this today?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.80,0:40:08.86,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Like I said many times,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.86,0:40:10.32,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,I cannot drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.32,0:40:11.79,Default,Kozo,0,0,0,,Just this one time, come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:11.79,0:40:14.47,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Shouldn't you listen to your doctor?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.15,0:40:21.88,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,So, let's just stick to one glass each.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.97,0:40:32.12,Default,Kozo,0,0,0,,Yukio.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:32.63,0:40:33.92,Default,Kozo,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.64,0:40:35.48,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:36.31,0:40:38.05,Default,Kozo,0,0,0,,You really helped me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:39.51,0:40:40.90,Default,Kozo,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.09,0:40:43.95,Default,Kozo,0,0,0,,I am truly sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.08,0:40:53.92,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,I don't know what you're talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.41,0:41:11.10,Bengoshi-Top,Rina,0,0,0,,They fell asleep so fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.57,0:41:14.20,Bengoshi-Top,Rina,0,0,0,,It hasn't even been ten minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.20,0:41:18.35,Bengoshi-Top,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Father, you shouldn't be sleeping here.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.57,0:41:20.92,Bengoshi-Top,Yoshie,0,0,0,,Look at them side-by-side.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.92,0:41:22.99,Bengoshi-Top,Yoshie,0,0,0,,They look so alike.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.99,0:41:25.31,Bengoshi-Top,Kanae,0,0,0,,They're father-son after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:30.17,0:41:31.40,Bengoshi-Top,Rina,0,0,0,,Horrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:31.40,0:41:32.75,Bengoshi-Top,Rina,0,0,0,,Water, water.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.72,0:41:36.81,Bengoshi-Top,Kanae,0,0,0,,I'm so glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.81,0:41:38.42,Bengoshi-Top,Yoshie,0,0,0,,About what?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:38.42,0:41:42.23,Bengoshi-Top,Kanae,0,0,0,,Sensei's been freed from \Nhis decades-long grudge.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.57,0:41:49.67,Bengoshi-Top,Kanae,0,0,0,,His parents' divorce must have driven \NSensei to become a divorce lawyer.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.67,0:41:51.97,Bengoshi-Top,Yoshie,0,0,0,,No, that wasn't it.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:51.97,0:41:53.24,Bengoshi-Top,Kanae,0,0,0,,What's the reason, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.20,0:41:55.27,Bengoshi-Top,Yoshie,0,0,0,,I wonder...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.89,0:41:59.47,Bengoshi-Top,Yoshie,0,0,0,,You should ask him about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:00.22,0:42:01.83,Bengoshi-Top,Yoshie,0,0,0,,Thanks for the wine.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.69,0:42:21.23,Bengoshi-Next_Episode,Caption,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,510)}Next episode
Dialogue: 0,0:42:10.06,0:42:13.85,Bengoshi-Top,Woman,0,0,0,,I can't find a marriage partner\N because of the marriage counselor!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:12.46,0:42:16.19,Bengoshi-End_Splash_Left,Caption,0,0,0,,Get compensation{\c&HE365A3&} from a crooked marriage counselor!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:13.85,0:42:16.71,Bengoshi-Top,Kurumi,0,0,0,,A dishonest marriage counselor \Nlike that should get punished!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:16.63,0:42:20.40,Bengoshi-End_Splash_Right,Caption,0,0,0,,Umemoto Kurumi's {\c&H4C3EDC&}Shocking Past Revealed!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:16.71,0:42:21.32,Bengoshi-Top,Yoshie,0,0,0,,I can't forgive people \Nwho look down on others.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:21.23,0:42:24.67,Bengoshi-Fiction,Caption,0,0,0,,{\fad(380,0)}This drama is a work of fiction
Dialogue: 0,0:42:21.32,0:42:24.64,Bengoshi-Top,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Win or lose, that's my responsibility.

